  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145190/extras/0eaebe6d66673da9e0a1a50de112717e.avif?t=1685538800\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>Energy Survivors is an action roguelite where you slay hordes of enemies and face bosses. Your only objective is to steal the energy of their planet and survive. Play as a mercenary, and with the spoils of every run upgrade your weapons, unlock new suits, and upgrade your skill tree.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Original soundtrack, designed to keep players fully immersed in the gameplay experience<br></li><li>Simple and intuitive controls that are easy to learn<br></li><li>Over 30 upgrades available for skills, weapons, and characters<br></li><li>Variety of Mutation Injectors to choose from, granting unique passive effects that change the gameplay experience in each run.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >shoot them all</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145190/extras/ddfea28db4a3ddb15d809804b0a745ac.poster.avif?t=1685538800\" width=600 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145190/extras/ddfea28db4a3ddb15d809804b0a745ac.webm?t=1685538800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145190/extras/ddfea28db4a3ddb15d809804b0a745ac.mp4?t=1685538800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose one upgrade</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145190/extras/b64219a15fc41e8d2efaea63172b0046.poster.avif?t=1685538800\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145190/extras/b64219a15fc41e8d2efaea63172b0046.webm?t=1685538800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145190/extras/b64219a15fc41e8d2efaea63172b0046.mp4?t=1685538800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Get powerful skills</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145190/extras/cfabc4b54bd314e9bd7239e3308b28dc.poster.avif?t=1685538800\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145190/extras/cfabc4b54bd314e9bd7239e3308b28dc.webm?t=1685538800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145190/extras/cfabc4b54bd314e9bd7239e3308b28dc.mp4?t=1685538800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>",
